Author: buzness-game
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: I understand the administration and I understand that the blogs and media paid a fixed number of tokens. But still think about it - from the pool MEDIA was paid only 2%, and this is 300 coins per article, whereas even social workers received 10,000 coins, and subscriptions average 40,000. What is 300 coins? Where is 98% blog pool? After a month everyone will break down and if $ goes for the article it will be simply delightful. In view of this, I still propose to the developer / manager to review the policy of blogs and pay coins at least to the level of social workers - this is x10 from the current award or count by the number of stacks is x50. I would very much like to hear the opinion of other media participants and the administrators about this.

Author: Kickico Bounty Hunter
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: We awarded blogs who presented good material. Just look at the blogs that were written - most of them were just copy paste from the website. There is no change in policy as it was all stated in bounty conditions.  But point taken, for blogs and media there should be some more criteria on how to assess the articles. We really worked with those who were writing good material, not just copying from the website.

Author: buzness-game
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: Yes ... Sadness sadness longing ... For subscription people were sent too much, and for media content of naughty, 800 coins per article with a banner for 2 months is ridiculous simply compared to 20 000 - 95 000 for signatures. And from the Media pool, 6,000,000 coins of payments for 130,000 - and this is 2% of the total pool, but the signers were paid a full percentage of their contribution. Moderator suggest that we revise the media policy and pay in shares or at least raise remuneration - to meet the minimum of signatures, but then it does not equal at all. We spent time and advertising space, and received a penny.

Author: Kickico Bounty Hunter
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: **KICKICO bounty update**  DEAR KICKICO BOUNTY PARTICIPANTS!  IMPORTANT STAKE POOLS UPDATE: During our ICO the hard cap of was lowered in half from 200k ETH to 100k ETH, so the total KickCoins supply accordingly reduced in half.  EVERYTHING was halved, including founders' pool too. So it's just denomination. Less tokens, higher price, easier for price to grow.  Following the KICK total supply reduction, Bounty pool with stake-wise awards was also reduced - Facebook, Twitter, Telegram and Signature.  This step was made to adjust the total supply of KickCoins and make it fair for all the tokens holders. Please note, since we reduced the total emission - KickCoins value will be higher for every holder - which is best for everyone.  Since we care about our backers and community and wish for KickCoins to grow as high as possible, we had to take the necessary steps for the benefit of all the participants.  Awards for stake-based campaigns will be calculated as follows: Facebook Pool - 750 000 KICK Twitter Pool - 750 000 KICK Telegram Pool - 250 000 KICK Signature Pool - 2 500 000 KICK  Bounty sheets are finalized for awards and stakes! Please check ETH addresses in the spreadsheets:  OLD REWARDS FOR KICKICO BOUNTY CAMPAIGN SPREADSHEET (before 26th of July) STAKES FOR FACEBOOK AND TWITTER SPREADSHEET REWARDS FOR ALL OTHER CAMPAIGNS SPREADSHEET  We give time till 30th of September for you to check the addresses - YOU HAVE TO OWN A PRIVATE KEY TO YOUR ADDRESS (exchanges or other wallets without private key - won't work!)  If you need to change the address post reply in this thread.  Bounty KickCoins will be distributed at the end of September - 1st week of October. Bounty pool tokens are frozen till 26th of November 2017. We thank everyone for participation in our bounty campaign and making this project a success!   Signatures stakes are calculated and signatures can be removed.

Author: Xavier59
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: Hey,  You should reconsider the bounty distribution. Translation campaign and bug bounty campaign seems clearly underevalued.  - Artwork : This category should never have existed.Well, let's consider artwork,  this one for example. I mean, come on, 30 000 kicktoken ? I didn't find a single gif that made me smile, sorry. There is nothing original.  - Bug bounty : Yes, I participated in this campaign, and I'm here to pledge my cause. Well, it actually cost me some times to test the application. Well, ~15k kicktoken are clearly not that bad. The bad thing is the payout compared to some others campaign. I've reported 2 vulns that could have allow me to steal funds, and I get half the amount of someone drawing random gifs ? Well in fact, 10k is not THAT bad. It's just bad compared to the other campaigns and the importance of security in ICOs. Meh. 22.500/5.000.000 tokens got distributed on this campaign. That's 0.45% of the allowed amount.    Well, there is the famous saying in french, broadly meaning Only the fools don't change their minds. It's not too late    - Translation : I didn't translate anything in that campaign. It's true that many use google translation. However, honest and hard working translators must not paid the price of all those fake translators. Translating is taking a lot of time. 6k seems a bit underevalued compared to others campaign. 10k seems more fair to me.  Still, wish you the best.

Author: Kickico Bounty Hunter
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: **KICKICO bounty update**  DEAR KICKICO BOUNTY PARTICIPANTS!  KICKICO bounty is over.  Bounty sheets are finalized for awards and stakes! Please check ETH addresses in the spreadsheets:  OLD REWARDS FOR KICKICO BOUNTY CAMPAIGN SPREADSHEET (before 26th of July) STAKES FOR FACEBOOK AND TWITTER SPREADSHEET REWARDS FOR ALL OTHER CAMPAIGNS SPREADSHEET  We give time till 30th of September for you to check the addresses - YOU HAVE TO OWN A PRIVATE KEY TO YOUR ADDRESS (exchanges or other wallets without private key - won't work!)  If you need to change the address post reply in this thread.  Bounty KickCoins will be distributed at the end of September - 1st week of October. Bounty pool tokens are frozen till 26th of November 2017. We thank everyone for participation in our bounty campaign and making this project a success!   Signatures stakes are calculated and signatures can be removed.

Author: Kickico Bounty Hunter
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: **KICKICO bounty update**  DEAR KICKICO BOUNTY PARTICIPANTS!  16th of September - last day of the bounty  All bounty rewards will be calculated in the bounty spreadsheet in the next 3-4 days. Please check the links on Bitcointalk thread.  Then we will give 1 more week for everyone to check their addresses and rewards for the work.  Bounty KickCoins will be distributed at the end of September.  Bounty pool tokens are frozen till 15th of November 2017.  We thank everyone for participation in our bounty campaign and making this project a success!

Author: wizardee
Title: [ KICKICO ] OFFICIAL BOUNTY CAMPAIGN THREAD
Body: Quote from: sergsen on July 28, 2017, 09:30:40 PM Week 3  Bitcointalk Username: sergsen Twitter URL: https://twitter.com/sergsen Followers: 4350 Please edit your post to the suitable format or we will not know how to pay you accordingly. Week Start - Week Finish WE NEED THE DATE, NOT JUST A WEEK NUMBER   Quote from: Disconnecting on July 28, 2017, 02:32:20 PM hi, joining your signature campaign  Great to have you on-board! Please fill out the application form.   Quote from: truncus on July 28, 2017, 05:43:07 PM Quote from: wizardee on July 28, 2017, 07:24:58 AM Quote from: truncus on July 27, 2017, 05:54:22 PM Quote from: Kickico Bounty Hunter on July 26, 2017, 06:53:36 AM  2 self tweets each week with hashtag #Kickico and 5 retweets every week we will get 1 stake. Why take 2 tweets per day?   Not exactly sure by what you are asking with the question. Why only 2 tweets? If so, then this is to stop a sudden spam of tweets. We would like the tweets to be spaced out evenly between each other and we figure this to be enough for us. If you want to post more, you can, but they will not be counted!   If we write more than 2 tweets per week, will we get stake?  If you qualify for the reward, you will be given stakes and your actual reward will be calculated at the end of the ICO. We only pay with stakes from 26. July. Your previous earnings will be added on top and calculated at the end. You will get stakes if you write 2 tweets - just remember to qualify and meet all points in the criteria.

Body: **KICKICO bounty update**  DEAR KICKICO BOUNTY PARTICIPANTS!  IMPORTANT UPDATE: BOUNTY REWARDS DISTRIBUTED -----------------------------  Telegram bounty of total pool 250 000 KICK is distributed and closed. Bounty is given to participants who were active on the main group @kickico till the end of ICO   -----------------------------  You can check the details for your rewards here: KICKICO BOUNTY CAMPAIGNS MASTER SPREADSHEET OLD REWARDS FOR KICKICO BOUNTY CAMPAIGN SPREADSHEET (before 26th of July)  We thank everyone for participation in our bounty campaign and making this project a success!   KickICO Bounty Program announcement   KickICO -  Single, Unified Platform for Cryptocurrency Crowdfunding Campaigns and ICOs  Anti Danilevski - Founder of KICKICO, 2017  WWW.KICKICO.COM  WHITEPAPPER    Chinese KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Dutch KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Filipino KickICO Bounty Campaign thread German KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Hindi KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Indonesian KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Japanese KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Italian KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Korean KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Portuguese KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Russian KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Scandinavian/Danish KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Spanish KickICO Bounty Campaign thread Turkish KickICO Bounty Campaign thread    Our Official  channels and groups: Bitcointalk.org  |  Facebook  |  Twitter  |  Telegram  |  Medium   Press about us: Forbes  |  Rusbase  |  Coinspeaker  |  Medium  |  DTF  |  E-pepper  |  PRweb  |  Huffingtonpost  |  Cointelegraph  |  Golos   KICKICO is a site for the automated and independent conducting of pre-ICO/ICO and launching of crowdfunding campaigns to collect funds in the form of cryptocurrencies. The purpose of KICKICO is to solve the aforementioned problems and create a single platform that will unite the authors and backers of ICO/crowdfunding campaigns to form an active, up-to-date community.   KickICO Bounty Program  We are announcing the launch of a KICKICO bounty program for everyone who wants to join our community and build with us the first crowdfunding ICO platform.   We have made an approximate forecast of an increase in KICK value. According to our plan, it will happen because the KICK price is now only 0.000167 ETH. The ICO price will be twice as high, with one KICK equal to 0.000333 ETH  _________________________________________________________________  KickICO Telegram   Telegram is the most convenient way for the fast communication with the hundreds of bounty campaign participants. It's impossible to answer all the questions quickly using forum PM and thread. Telegram team channels and private chats are much better for this.  _________________________________________________________________  KickICO project bounty manager and support account: KickICO Support   All the questions regarding KickICO bounty campaign should be addressed to the KickICO Support account. Thx.  OLD REWARDS FOR KICKICO BOUNTY CAMPAIGN SPREADSHEET (before 26th of July)  STAKES FOR FACEBOOK AND TWITTER SPREADSHEET  REWARDS FOR ALL OTHER CAMPAIGNS SPREADSHEET  TO GET YOUR REWARDS YOU HAVE TO SUBMIT REPORTS HERE IN THE THREAD WITH PROOF-LINKS OF YOUR WORK REWARDS SHEET IS UPDATED ON SUNDAY EVERY WEEK, SO PLEASE SUBMIT YOUR REPORTS BEFORE WEEKEND  Join our campaigns and get reward for your contribution!      Community Management Campaign Pool: 4 500 000 KickCoins ---> NEW Registration closed !!!  Help us explain to other users how KICKICO works. We'll judge by the activity on the forum and results, rewards may vary accordingly. Community management requires not only to moderate, but to interract with users, develop brand awareness and popularity and so on.   Bounty:  Bitcointalk community management [500 КC, weekly payment] Telegram channel community management [250 КC, weekly payment] Reddit community management [500 КC, weekly payment] Telegram official channel joining: KICKICO - Official (eng) [10 КC]   Restrictions:  Multiple accounts registrations Spam, abuse and insults   Terms and conditions:  BCT: Only for BTT Full Members and up BCT: Make at least 50 publications on Bitcointalk within KICKICO topic page during the campaign. Reddit: 100k+ karma required Reddit: Post must be in a subreddit with over 100 readers. Your must be in Telegram group until end of KICKICO ICO campaign: KICKICO - Official (eng)      Bitcointalk Signature and Avatar Campaign Pool: 5 000 000 KickCoins --->   NEW Registration closed !!!  We are looking for the active Bitcointalk users. All members need to post at least 15 posts a week having the KickICO signature by the time the KickICO ICO ends to be eligible for a reward.   Bounty:   Set up KICKICO signature and avatar to your Bitcointalk profile: Junior Members : 1 stakes per week Members : 2 stakes per week Senior/Full : 4 stakes per week Legendary/Hero: 6 stakes per week  Posts in this thread will not count.  Stake will be added in Rewards Sheet Sunday to Sunday.     Restrictions:  Negative trust Multiple signatures Signature and/or avatar change during the campaign Posts in following Discussion Boards: Politics and Society, Off-topic, Archival, Auctions, Lending, Beginners and help Spam, abuse and insults     Terms and conditions:  Only for BTT  Jn.Members and up Make at least 15 posts each week during the campaign Posts in alternate cryptocurrencies section are required. Posts in any bounty thread will not count. Participants are rewarded according their rank Spam is strictly prohibited. Users found spamming will be immediately and permanently disqualified, reported to the moderators, and banned from any other bounty campaign.
